textAnnotations.description:
HORRID HENRY'S
NEWSPAPER
wi noe fair buled Horrid fenry
Vwar a Mip-Hop Robor dog
Horrid Henry nended money Lon
and ke and Aon of money His parents
dide eed moey and yer they had
Ad move than he did. Ir war so untair
Wly was he so bralliant at pndiny
money, and so bud at gemie money?
And now Mum and Dad refed ao buy
his something he deperately needed
Kou huve plenty of toys, said Mum
Which you nevrr play with said Dad
